name: Badges
description:
Choose from one of our fun designs or create a custom design.

Each badge is made when you order.

Check out our Facebook page to see some of the amazing images available

http://www.facebook.com
/bitsandbobsbrisbane

The bandges are light weight.
They are made of rubber with a photo paper image attached.

Postage- Australia -$2
              International -$3

(when posted with others items add 50c to postage costs)

Our payment method is Paypal

When ordering-
please email us at bitsandbobsbrisbane@gmail.com what design you are after or the image you would like on the custom badge.

Why not order a matching keyring or earrings!
